title: Ep. 1270 - An Envelope Of Cash - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide finds an envelope of cash in the wardrobe and questions Madhvi. She tells him that it's her money and Bhide gets offended. She tells him her plan of having a kitty party and going for lunch with the ladies of the society.

title: Ep. 1271 - The Ladies Brunch - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: All the ladies of the Gokuldham society are ready to go out and have lunch. They reach the hotel and have a welcome drink. They are all excited and ready to have fun.

title: Ep. 1272 - Investing The Money - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Madhvi tells everyone that they have collected a lot of money and asks them what to do about the money.

title: Ep. 1273 - The Necklace Situation - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Babita comes up with an idea to get the necklace from Rakesh. Everyone agrees with her and fix on a neckless. After getting the necklace, Daya tells everyone that Madhavi will be the first one to wear it.

title: Ep. 1274 - Fake Necklace - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya finds out that a person who sold them the Necklace was fake. Jetha introduces the real Rakesh to her.

title: Ep. 1275 - Catching The Culprit - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The ladies figure out who the culprit is and plot a plan to catch him. Everyone gets furious and goes to the hotel to find him.

title: Ep. 1276 - The Grand Plan - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: All the ladies pray to the Lord to help them with the plan of catching the culprit. They all lie to their husbands to get out and go ahead with the plan. They book tables in the same hotel and try to fool the culprit waiter. Will their plan work?

title: Ep. 1277 - Daya's Great Act - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya dresses up as someone else and goes to the hotel. She pretends to be on the call and give off details regarding the money. The waiter takes the bait and sends his guy to the location. Will they catch the culprit?

title: Ep. 1278 - Daya's Special Dish - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: After catching the culprit Daya returns home and back to all her usual chores. She cooks delicious food for Jetha

title: Ep. 1279 - Onion Issue - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Champaklal aggressively puts his point before everyone as onions price should not be increasing. Daya and Jetha discuss the same. Bhide cannot find onion in Poha and asks Madhvi about it. Madhvi tells him about the hike in onion prices.

title: Ep. 1280 - Police In The City - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha is shocked to see the high security in the city. He impresses Pandey with his words. Pandey informs Jetha that people in the city are hiding onion and are trying to sell it in black.

title: Ep. 1281 - Police Inspects Gada Electronics- Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Police visit the Gada electronics shop and ask Jetha to make him visit his godown as well. Baga warns the police not to go there as he might find the rats. However, the police decide to inspect his godown. Nattu kaka defends Jethalal.

title: Ep. 1282 - Bagha Gets Arrested - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak arrives to help Jetha get out of the situation. Pandey arrests Bagha and asks for proof if they want to release him.

title: Ep. 1283 - Daya Breaks Champaklal's Glasses - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Champaklal looks for his glasses and asks Daya for help. Daya tells him that it broke unintentionally.

title: Ep. 1284 - Baawri Is Found - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone found Baawri and asks her the reason behind Baga getting arrested. Baawri explains to them how his brother Chandu wanted to sell onions in black and in order to not let him do so, she took Baga's help for hiding the onions in the Gada shop.
